REMARK 245  CORRESPONDING TO A PHYSICAL PIXEL SIZE OF 0.844 A/PX                
REMARK 245  (SUPERRESOLUTION PIXEL SIZE 0.422 A/PX) IN CDS MODE AT A DOSE       
REMARK 245  RATE OF 9.5 E-/PX/S (~7.5 E-/PX/S ON THE CAMERA THROUGH THE         
REMARK 245  SAMPLE) AND A DEFOCUS RANGE OF -0.5 TO -1.8 MICROMETER USING        
REMARK 245  SERIALEM. IN TOTAL, 2,653 AND 8,443 MOVIES WERE COLLECTED IN TWO    
REMARK 245  SEPARATE IMAGING SESSIONS, WITH THE FIRST DATASET ON A 400-MESH     
REMARK 245  COPPER GRID AND THE SECOND ON A 300-MESH ULTRAUFOIL GOLD GRID.      
